    Place(name: 'The Landmark Nicosia', imagePath: 'NicosiaHotels/TheLandMark.jpg', lat: 35.15934584378223, long:33.37199582726373, city: 'Nicosia', category: '5 Star Hotel', id: 58, description: 'The Landmark Nicosia in Cyprus offers a range of comfortable and luxurious accommodation options. Their King Guest room and Twin Guest Room Pool View are both equipped with premium bedding, minibar, in-room safe, and free toiletries. For families or those seeking more space, the Family Room and various suites, including the Deluxe Suite (King) and Presidential Suite, provide ample room and added luxury. All rooms come with city views and are designed with comfort and elegance in mind. The hotel also features an indoor pool, free parking, and other amenities to enhance your stay (photo from Tripadvisor)'),
    Place(name: 'Madama Residence', imagePath: 'NicosiaHotels/madama.jpg', lat:35.17203217357559, long:33.3621101524108 , id: 59, city: 'Nicosia', category: '5 Star Hotel', description: 'The Madama Residence in Nicosia, Cyprus, is a highly-rated boutique hotel, boasting an impressive score of 9.3 out of 10 from guests. It is celebrated for its exceptional staff, quality facilities, high cleanliness standards, comfort, and good value for money. The location of the hotel is particularly appreciated by guests, earning a score of 9.2 out of 10.The hotel is located in the heart of Nicosia’s vibrant and atmospheric Old Town, occupying a building that was once Cyprus’ first bakery and mill. This heritage site has been transformed into a luxurious and contemporary accommodation option. The hotel offers six high-end suites, each with its own unique character and style, providing a sophisticated, adults-only haven. The suites blend tradition, comfort, and style in a harmonious balance( photo from Booking).')
